name: The End Of Times Burger (POWER BITCOIN XXL)
description:
The POWER BITCOIN XXL represents the energy consumption of new technologies, that can change the world or destroy it, depends on our consciousness and intelligence the fate of our planet as well as our survival as a species.

All the ingredients of each hamburger are elements that in some way,
they negatively influence our environment and threaten our existence.
Would you do something to change it?
